short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension sorts your bookmarks by most recently used.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension shows your most recently accessed bookmarks (starting from when the extension was installed) at the top of your bookmarks list. You can also protect some bookmarks so they always show up at the top.  

In order to sort bookmarks, the extension needs access to your browsing activity.  

This extension was initially created by a team of three people. See the GitHub here: https://github.com/TheLingo1/Bookmark-Auto-Organizer
